1
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,840
Hand over the antidote.

2
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:06,480
Otherwise, I'll send you to hell right now.

3
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,580
This poison is called Liangxinmian.

4
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:12,160
The antidote must be taken

5
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,000
