28
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,800
Alright, I still have to rely on our Divine Doctor Yan.

29
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,560
Of course.

30
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,120
You...

31
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,920
Didn't you already take the antidote pill?

32
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:46,920
