33
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,280
Let me see.

34
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,400
Your pulse...

35
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,920
doesn't seem like...

36
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,280
I...

37
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,640
I'm actually fine.

38
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,420
Your Highness,

39
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,200
we've shaken off the pursuers outside.

40
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,040
I got it.

41
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,560
You've shaken off the pursuers?

42
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,000
Yes, we did.

43
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:46,920
All of them.

44
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,880
You already took the antidote,

45
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,240
yet you faked a poison attack.

46
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,640
You have ulterior motives, Your Highness.

47
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,940
If I didn't do this,

48
00:04:58,159 --> 00:05:00,420
