49
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,160
Miss Yan is incredibly smart,

50
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:05,730
and you are quite the schemer, Your Highness.

51
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,280
This marriage,

52
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,880
I'm afraid the Matchmaker carefully calculated it

53
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,000
