56
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,920
I am willing to take the punishment.

57
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,480
Your Highness, it's getting late.

58
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,240
I'll go escort Miss Yan.

59
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:18,760
