116
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,200
From now on,

117
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,120
without my permission,

118
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,480
you cannot

119
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,760
